    <h3 class="cmp-teaser__title h--smaller" data-titlerow="One" data-titlerowlaptop="One" data-titlerowtablet="One">
        Harvard Medical School Studies Protein Interactions at an Unprecedented Pace Using NVIDIA DGX Cloud
    </h3>

        
    <div class="cmp-teaser__description">
    	
       		<p>The National Science Foundation’s National Artificial Intelligence Research Resource (NAIRR) pilot program with access to NVIDIA DGX™ Cloud, The Walter Lab at Harvard Medical School completed nearly 1.7 million protein interaction predictions in 3 months.</p>
        
    </div>

        
	
	
	
