    </h3>

        
    <div class="cmp-teaser__description">
    	
       		<p>Researchers at the University of Maryland, recipients of a grant from the NVIDIA Academic Grant Program, are developing AI-powered humanoid systems capable of complex household tasks with greater autonomy. Using the NVIDIA Isaac™ open robotics development platform, they create photorealistic virtual home environments populated with diverse objects, allowing robots to practice millions of task variations and safely test rare or complex scenarios.</p>
        
