    </h3>

        
    <div class="cmp-teaser__description">
    	
       		<p>A joint team at BRLi and National Polytechnic Institute of Toulouse (Toulouse INP), through a collaboration in the ANITI research institute, has designed an end-to-end AI approach that fully replaces the physics-based solver. This team includes expertise in both hydraulic modeling and AI methods for physics, enabling this interdisciplinary work. The Toulouse INP team then used these to train an end-to-end AI system to emulate the solver leveraging NVIDIA PhysicsNeMo from the Earth-2 platform.</p>
        
