       		<p>Miles College launched “Access for All,” supporting up to 750 underserved Alabama high school students with AI workforce training. Developed with NVIDIA and StudyFetch under the White House Pledge to America’s Youth, the program uses NVIDIA Academy and Deep Learning Institute content to build practical AI skills.</p>
        
