        AI Foundation Model GluFormer Outperforms Clinical Standards in Forecasting Diabetes and Cardiovascular Risk
    </h3>

        
    <div class="cmp-teaser__description">
    	
       		<p>GluFormer, developed by MBZUAI and the Weizmann Institute, predicts diabetes and cardiovascular risk from just 10–14 days of glucose data. It outperforms the clinical standard HbA1c, identifying 66% of future diabetes cases and 69% of cardiovascular-death events across 19 diverse global cohorts.</p>
        
    </div>

        
	
	
	
